While this repository provides the raw calculation logic, the full featured tools (including PDF Reporting, Visual Charts, and Dark Mode UI) are available for free on our official platform.

Official Tools:

Absence Percentage Calculator - Includes downloadable PDF reports for HR documentation.

InterCalculator Homepage - Access the full suite of financial and utility tools.

Contributing
Pull requests are welcome. For major changes regarding the core formulas, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change.

